  "text": "C57BL/6 and BtkÀ/À mice were generated as previously described [CITATION_1] and were bred and maintained at the Experimental Animal Center (EDC) of the Erasmus MC, Rotterdam, The Netherlands under specified pathogen-free condition. All procedures were approved by the Animal Ethics committee (DEC) of the Erasmus MC.",
